item.title: Server Won't Start

item.description:

hmm…I can help.Do you have teamviewer, if not then i canz help thru here.Try checking if utorrent is running on portforwarding(ctrl and p,then connection and check if that port says 43594.), if so click “Randomize Port” then apply then ok.The in your system bar (/), right click utorrent and click exit and click ok.

item.title: Server Won't Start
item.dc:creator: @ry60003333 ry60003333
item.description:
@ry60003333 wrote:

Something is already running on port 43594, or something is blocking the socket from binding to that port. Try restarting the computer and disabling security settings.
